org.apache.flink.runtime.rest.messages

接口 MessageHeaders<R extends RequestBody,P extends ResponseBody,M extends MessageParameters>

  • 类型参数:
    R - request message type
    P - response message type
    M - message parameters type
    所有超级接口:
    RestHandlerSpecification
    所有已知实现类:
    BlobServerPortHeaders, CheckpointConfigHeaders, CheckpointingStatisticsHeaders, CheckpointStatisticDetailsHeaders, ClusterConfigurationInfoHeaders, ClusterOverviewHeaders, CurrentJobsOverviewHandlerHeaders, DashboardConfigurationHeaders, JobConfigHeaders, JobExceptionsHeaders, JobPlanHeaders, JobSubmitHeaders, JobTerminationHeaders, JobVertexAccumulatorsHeaders, SavepointTriggerHeaders, TaskCheckpointStatisticsHeaders

    public interface MessageHeaders<R extends RequestBody,P extends ResponseBody,M extends MessageParameters>
extends RestHandlerSpecification
    This class links RequestBodys to ResponseBodys types and contains meta-data required for their http headers.

    Implementations must be state-less.
